The Omnisharp extension won't pickup the solution in this folder if there is not a csproj file in the same directory.
With multiroot workspaces, it also won't pick up solution files in the workspace root, so it has to be in a project folder.
Similarly, the 'Solution Explorer' extension doesn't pickup solutions in the root either. It only finds solutions in the
FIRST project folder, so we list 'Solution' as the first project in the workspace